This paper focuses on software code reviews and algorithms for recommending appropriate code reviewers. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. However, it also involves data mining and information retrieval techniques (cs.IR), machine learning algorithms (cs.LG), social and information networks (cs.SI), and cybernetics (cs.CY) in order to analyze and compare the performance of different recommendation algorithms.
